{"tid":1458392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我愛香港！！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:12:13.000Z","uid":242805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c9de8710beb591ff82801716b3728bdf333e65","tid":1458392,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:52:24.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得香港人好中意屌來屌去？<br />\n<br />\n一個地方有咁多唔同種族，各自有唔同意見好正常，大家點解唔理性溝通，成日屌來屌去，覺得人地做法唔岩嘅時間，你可以表達你嘅意見，一齊討論，但就唔好開口埋口屌老母，記住我地共同敵人係邊個！！！<br />\n鬧手足無用！佢要堅持留，就要為自己決定負責，大家唔係三歲小朋友，識得諗，記住自己獨立思考，唔好過份相信身邊人！<br />\n我知大家擔心安全，但勸唔掂都唔好鬧！未打到嚟 自己人已經屌死自己人。<br />\n<br />\n記住一齊槍口對外！一齊努力！<br />\n<br />\n加油香港人！我愛大家！記住香港仲有愛 大家多d表達愛意，唔好成日鬧自己人！<br />\n<br />\n最尾 娘都要講句 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">團結就是力量！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160352906f40447eb8656e9891c104cd6934c97e","tid":1458392,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a80e6185784ed892ee7f77986137f6a019828668","tid":1458392,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2188dacbe302cece7bc8595f72cacede455ac35d","tid":1458392,"uid":193961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:54:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"223d9c872ffa0c714def54fecfb1031b900f96a0","tid":1458392,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"278b8c728b66d8e7069f3ce52fcb82ba09b57827","tid":1458392,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5360df4095b6939ddb8b617b09c865c0aa5364d","tid":1458392,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" cla